578a","tid":570512,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3079dc97be812fd4007ce7bda4ed2288d2e0939c","tid":570512,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:50:14.000Z","msg":"鬼佬完全唔理粒制，以前公司橦大廈八成都係鬼佬，第一日返工仲諗做乜個個鬼佬搭𨋢都發夢<br />\n<br />\n然後每次我撳關門制佢地個樣都覺得我好趕咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"可能佢地覺得香港人生活節奏急速掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4705d4bb62d1aaad8c22ed4cbbceff8f958477","tid":570512,"uid":140198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"443614dc63f8657ddb15d2ecf43023c0a5b2b19a","tid":570512,"uid":8534,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0ebfe04caa509c550c62d80f7bc02f1a12665649","tid":570512,"uid":129660,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"我準備出lift果陣，條友隻手擺定係關門制<br />\n感覺唔係好舒服，係咪好多人都係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"只要佢冇係你出緊嗰時㩒就得啦，佢應該係趕時間姐我諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"個人黎講幾趕時間都唔會咁做 好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等到人地出左lift門先伸手準備㩒 最多咪慢個零點幾秒 反正點都要等人出晒去先 正如上面咁講 唔會真係出緊個時㩒黎夾人㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好多人都咁樣擺定隻手 雖然知人地無惡意 但自己心裡唔好受 <br />\n<br />\n所以將心比己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34345e985ef83ef6e79b41193ae83a74eeaf272a","tid":570512,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ebfe04caa509c550c62d80f7bc02f1a12665649","tid":570512,"uid":129660,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"我準備出lift果陣，條友隻手擺定係關門制<br />\n感覺唔係好舒服，係咪好多人都係咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"住頂樓冇體驗過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a996fece9c90fb9647847b0833eb2272f510f8e3","tid":570512,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02